車定私家車? <br />\nA:台中台南多數用機車，台北多數捷運。(BY 傲世三界巴打) <br />\n<br />\nQ:台妹點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nA:肯_定好過港女先(BY 傲世三界巴打) <br />\n<br />\nQ:大學生活點? <br />\nA:一定要同台仔打好關係，佢地會帶你去玩同識囡囡，多參加學校社團，好多學校社團對港澳生有超級唔好嘅印象，原因係好冇交帶，普通話其實唔洗好好，不過佢地都要聽得明。(BY 傲世三界巴打) <br />\n<br />\nQ:台灣大學上堂用國語定英語？<br />\nA:國立既大多英書中教，考試用中定英就睇教授。(BY一生只有妳 )</blockquote><br />\n依家唔係唔比你sell台灣升學呀 喂大佬你唔好乜撚台灣post都貼呢篇野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 煩唔煩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d8c3faec5c5cc0ce45756772994e1d8fe0033f","tid":313044,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"相濡以&quot;味&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd9615bb639fac14be4ee543c462cd4eae37506","tid":313044,"uid":8081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabb85f880a482b4e3a8315f94b9d74d2364c84d","tid":313044,"uid":94457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:33:43.000Z","msg":"相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148e9a81334dbc7b0ae490f407f2acb81d0aeaed","tid":313044,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:35:00.000Z","msg":"架機場捷運明明係新，都成陣公廁味"},{"pid":"d5cce8ccec199fb95cd893937bedff28320998f8","tid":313044,"uid":394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci